---
import Icon from '@components/Icon.astro';
import { waLink } from '@/consts';
---

<section class='px-6 pb-16'>
	<div
		class='relative mx-auto max-w-[1180px] overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] bg-gradient-to-br from-copper to-copper-dark px-[clamp(28px,5vw,64px)] py-[clamp(48px,6vw,84px)] text-center'
	>
		<!-- decorative circles -->
		<div
			class='pointer-events-none absolute -left-10 -top-20 size-[240px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.08]'
			aria-hidden='true'>
		</div>
		<div
			class='pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-[100px] -right-[30px] size-[280px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.07]'
			aria-hidden='true'>
		</div>

		<div class='relative'>
			<h2
				class='mx-auto mb-[18px] max-w-[660px] font-heading text-[clamp(30px,4.2vw,52px)] font-semibold leading-[1.06] tracking-[-0.5px] text-white'
			>
				¿Listo para dar el paso?
			</h2>
			<p class='mx-auto mb-[34px] max-w-[560px] text-[clamp(17px,1.5vw,20px)] font-normal leading-[1.65] text-[#fbf3ea]'>
				Escríbenos y te decimos qué tenemos disponible hoy. Sin compromiso, con la confianza de una asesoría cercana.
			</p>
			<a
				href={waLink()}
				target='_blank'
				rel='noopener'
				class='inline-flex items-center gap-[11px] rounded-full bg-white px-9 py-[18px] text-[17px] font-extrabold text-copper-deep shadow-[0_18px_40px_-16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5'
			>
				<Icon
					name='whatsapp'
					size={26}
				/>
				Consultar disponibilidad por WhatsApp
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
